113
00:11:14,050 --> 00:11:16,050
Dia berpura-pura menjadi teman.

114
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:18,589
Dia menipumu, Bodoh.

115
00:11:19,959 --> 00:11:21,489
Itu pendapatmu.

116
00:11:21,489 --> 00:11:23,599
Kamu lebih buruk, dasar penipu.

117
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:26,060
Apa? Penipu?

118
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,810
"Mun Tae Rang"

